data.title: Heretics of Dune by Frank Herbert
data.meta_description: A wiki dedicated to providing trigger warnings, tropes, and controversies for any given book.
data.text:
Heretics of Dune by Frank Herbert is an adult science fiction novel, originally published on April 1st 1984. It is the fifth book in the Dune series.
